ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7af7221870d9636186f1767cb08700944fcb70","tid":217274,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早兩年有好多做藥既行家話有得做，d商會重要搞考察團去睇。好彩當時無踩隻腳入去，唔係就肯定蝕死。</blockquote><br />\n因這類貨品須由廠方向海關提供成分證明等資料，廠方絕大部分都耍手擰頭，故不可能取得商貿批文。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係要俾哂成份支共抄藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸典型投倆<br />\n口講益你去投資 大把機遇<br />\n到你投資完就過橋抽板 係另一度屈鳩你錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8f6e4d72445d4d34c7924f9f642a7a9fe4c687","tid":217274,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:02:57.000Z","msg":"關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895b8f50b2b2bb0400ecff39b23a0e7227ade16b","tid":217274,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野前海 大灣 一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本精人出口 笨人出手</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吹左幾年咪搵個新故仔<br />\n<br />\nbtw支那咁撚威都要抄香港街名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e0d18859a53427c15968cdbf43458af2c8a58e","tid":217274,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:08:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話超越左紐約倫敦既</blockquote><br />\n騙人的手法的確超越左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff700e9e2b555d95905755100c74264f9f6007e7","tid":217274,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:14:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>「西部大開發」人流不似預期　港商無得賺感心淡 <br />\n「大珠三角」人流不似預期　港商無得賺感心淡 <br />\n「泛珠三角」人流不似預期　港商無得賺感心淡 <br />\n「9+2」人流不似預期　港商無得賺感心淡 <br />\n「一帶一路」人流不似預期　港商無得賺感心淡 <br />\n「大灣區」人流不似預期　港商無得賺